"779","<DESCRIPTION>LEGAL LETTER"
"780","<TEXT>"
"781","SUB-ITEM 77E:  LEGAL PROCEEDINGS"
"782","Since February 2004, Federated and related"
"783","entities (collectively, ?Federated?) have been"
"784","named as defendants in several lawsuits, that were"
"785","consolidated into a single action in the United"
"786","States District Court for the Western District of"
"787","Pennsylvania, alleging excessive advisory fees"
"788","involving one of the Federated-sponsored mutual"
"789","funds.  Without admitting the validity of any claim,"
"790","Federated reached a final settlement with the"
"791","Plaintiffs in these cases in April 2011."
